OL,3,CMore job losses as Jersey Airport's
OL,4,Conly convenience store to shut
OL,6,FJersey Airport's only convenience
OL,7,Fstore, WHSmith, will close on Monday
OL,8,F22 September as part of plans to
OL,9,Fredevelop the departures terminal.
OL,11,FIt comes after 18 people were made
OL,12,Fredundant last week, following a
OL,13,Fdecision by Airline Services Channel
OL,14,FIslands Limited to close the Executive
OL,15,FLounge.
