OL,3,CMore job losses as Jersey Airport's
OL,4,Conly convenience store to shut
OL,6,FOnce WHSmith shuts, Ports of Jersey
OL,7,Fsays passengers will not be able to
OL,8,Fpurchase books and magazines until
OL,9,Fsummer 2026 and that "there will be a
OL,10,Fshort gap in the supply of some health
OL,11,Fand beauty travel essentials".
OL,13,FIt adds that urgent items such as
OL,14,Fnappies, sanitary products and baby
OL,15,Ffood will be provided for free by
OL,16,Fairport staff upon request.
OL,18,FFood and drink can still be bought
OL,19,Ffrom Cafe Ube, which will also start
OL,20,Fstocking a selection of newspapers.
