OL,3,CMore job losses as Jersey Airport's
OL,4,Conly convenience store to shut
OL,6,FMeanwhile, World Duty Free will
OL,7,Fcontinue to sell toys and tech
OL,8,Fproducts.
OL,10,FThe changes are part of a major
OL,11,Fproject to update the 28-year-old
OL,12,Fdeparture hall facilities, including a
OL,13,Fnew restaurant, free runway views and
OL,14,Fdedicated quiet zones.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Ports of Jersey says:
OL,17,F"The WHSmith store at Jersey Airport
OL,18,Fwill be closing as part of our planned
OL,19,Fredevelopment of the terminal,
OL,20,Fdesigned to transform the customer and
OL,21,Fretail experience.
