OL,4,Conly convenience store to shut
OL,6,F"This decision also reflects valuable
OL,7,Ffeedback from our customers, which we
OL,8,Ftake very seriously.
OL,10,F"We recognise that this change affects
OL,11,Fa number of staff employed by WHSmith,
OL,12,Fand we are committed to supporting
OL,13,Fthem during this transition.
OL,15,F"This closure is part of our wider
OL,16,Finvestment programme to enhance the
OL,17,Ffacilities at Jersey Airport."
OL,19,FIt has not been confirmed how many
OL,20,Fstaff will lose their jobs as a result
OL,21,Fof the WHSmith closure.
